name: Rob Bonta
tweet: One year ago, @GavinNewsom selected me to serve as California’s Attorney General.   Now, I go into work every day to lead a team of public servants dedicated to fighting for the health and safety of ALL Californians.   I am incredibly proud of what we have accomplished together.

name: Rob Bonta
tweet: So now, as we celebrate the ACA today, it’s also time to look forward to the fight ahead.   Each and every person deserves access to care.   We can’t stop working until this is a reality.  #ACAHereToStay

name: Rob Bonta
tweet: Despite endless court challenges and Republican opposition the ACA has survived.    Last June, the Supreme Court ruled in our case defending the ACA, affirming—for hopefully the last time—that the ACA is the law of the land. #ACAHereToStay

name: Rob Bonta
tweet: 12 years.  For 12 years the Affordable Care Act has expanded access to quality, affordable healthcare for people across the country.   This means 12 years of reproductive care, check-ups, & needed treatments for illness for people who could otherwise not afford it. #ACAHereToStay
